{"tid":2370295,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支那日常】網友報告QQ掃描並上傳用戶的瀏覽器歷史","createTime":"2021-01-18T02:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T06:06:34.000Z","uid":135110,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6332d3ae679df6fa275183c4f263394efe3e0fd5","tid":2370295,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:36:56.000Z","msg":"品玩1月18日訊，騰訊消息應用 QQ 以及 QQ 辦公版 TIM 被發現會掃描用戶的瀏覽器歷史，搜尋購物記錄選擇性上傳。近日，在V2EX論壇上，有網友反映發現聊天軟件QQ嘗試讀取用戶瀏覽記錄的問題，被該名網友發現。 QQ 在登入10分鐘之後開始掃描Appdata\\Local\\下的所有資料夾，對其中User Data\\Default\\History 進行進一步的掃描，User Data\\Default\\History 是基於Chrome/Chromium 的瀏覽器預設歷史紀錄存放位置，Firefox 的瀏覽歷史存放位置不同，因此目前看來不受影響。不過 Firefox 市場份額不高，而基於 Chrome/Chromium 的瀏覽器佔據了九成以上的份額。<br />\n<br />\n此前，媒體也報導過，騰訊QQ瀏覽器因未授權同意就獲取用戶信息的行為，被用戶訴至法院併申請訴前行為保全，法院裁定其立即停止相關行為。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <code>\nhttps://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-01-18/doc-ikftpnnx8666213.shtml\n</code><br />\n<br />\n相關技術分析：<br />\n<a href=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a9e20afa2198d7f59148b2f2e687c9be_r.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic1.zhimg.com%2Fv2-a9e20afa2198d7f59148b2f2e687c9be_r.jpg&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9fEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=baca56c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a9e20afa2198d7f59148b2f2e687c9be_r.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"5ba41a7a3e0c40a11f0f4c4aacc9654317dbc967","tid":2370295,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7931bec66c846cf79f8221ea379bc3688084ce","tid":2370295,"uid":61974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:51:12.000Z","msg":"支那人唔係話行得正企得正怕咩比人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji